name: TrapEndTypes
shortdesc: Shape options for the intersection of three-way traps.

property.name: MITER_TRAP_ENDS
property.shortdesc: Shapes the end of the trap to keep it away from the intersecting object.

property.name: OVERLAP_TRAP_ENDS
property.shortdesc: Reshapes the trap generated by the lightest neutral density object so that it wraps around the point where the three objects intersect.
